\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Convinces the male controllers of images and wealth that she is reducible to current sexual fashion, available to the male on his own terms, she is paid and honored. Her acting must be imitative, not creative; rigidly confomring, not self generated adn self renewing. The actress is the puppet of flesh, blood, and paint who acts as if she is the female acting. She died alone, possible acting on her own behalf for the the first time. Death, one imagines , numbs the pain that barbiturates and alcohol cannot touch.}
