\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Women experience the world as mystery. Kept ignorant of technology, economics, most of the practiccal skills required to function autonomously, kept ignorant of the real social andsexual demands mode on women, deprived of physical strength, excluded from forums for the development of intellectual acuity, and public self-confidence, women are lost and mystified by the savage momentum of an ordinary life. Sounds, signs, proomises, threats, wildly crisscross, but what do they mean? The right offers women a simple, fixed, predetermined social, biological, and sexulal order. Form conquers chaos. Form banishes confusion. Form gives ignorance a shape, makes it look like something instead of nothing. }
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Safteyl. For women, the world is a very dangerous place. On wrong move, even an unintentional smile, can bring disaster \hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0  assault, shame, disgrace. The right acknoledges the reality of danger, teh validity of fear. The right then manipulates the fear. The promise is that if a woman is obedient, harm will not befall her.}
